{
  "stem": "5758.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to pay quite a bit of money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went to Aachen at night, and there we were assembled in a barn, you know, a farm.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he told us, you must be very, very quiet, and we'll walk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I will show you where to walk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And nobody, but nobody, was allowed to make a move or cry or-- or-- or say anything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were approximately-- we were approximately 20 people, 20 Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he took us, at night, through a forest, and it was quite traumatic, actually, the fear of being discovered and-- and-- but he pointed out to us that the-- the main thing is that you avoid the Belgium, because if they catch you they may well return you.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he told us exactly where to go, and we went to a village, forgotten the name, where they put us into a private car, you know, several private cars.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Took us to the biggest town nearby, and we took the train and went to Brussels.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I must say, this Fraulein Schiff, that was our neighbor, gave me the address of her-- another cousin who lives in Antwerp by the name of Joss Apte, A-P-T-E, who was a diamond merchant in Antwerp.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She-- I arrived in Antwerp somewhere around in the region of 7:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had the address, and I went to that-- I always forget-- I'll always remember [NON-ENGLISH]-- in-- in [FLEMISH], in Flemish it is [FLEMISH]-- and beautiful building, you know, apartment house.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's 7:00, and I was hungry and cold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And said, it's too early, really, to ring the bell.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But at 7:30, I couldn't stand it anymore, and-- and I rang the bell, and they opened up.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
